decks.notes: The deck focuses on utilizing the companion Jegantha, the Wellspring to generate mana and enable powerful combos with cards like Collected Company, Atraxa, Grand Unifier, and Kinnan, Bonder Prodigy. The deck also includes various mana dorks and ramp spells to accelerate into its key combo pieces. Other cards like Relic of Legends and Honest Rutstein offer additional utility and support for the combo strategy. The mana base includes a mix of dual lands and utility lands to ensure consistency and flexibility in casting spells.
